name: ExecuSys, Inc.
tag_list: software, performance, performance-based-contracting, financial, government, cost-accounting, maximo-work-order-management, emergency-operations, dcaa, knowledge-management, business-intelligence
overview:
ExecuSys, Inc. is a software engineering solutions provider to the Federal Government.

ExecuSys specializes in business intelligence, knowledge management, and decision support systems. The company provides proven software solutions in: (1) Government cost accounting and financial systems; (2) Integrated Maximo work order management systems; (3) Enterprise portal integration; (4) Emergency Operations Center web applications; (5) Knowledge Management Frameworks and; (6) Performance based contract management tools.
